about.summary: Fast db insert with postgresql binary copy

name: pgcopy
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pgcopy" %}
{% set version = "1.4.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: "e71f84807559f5d13549e8cf690d29c220b704f950c3060cf7cc5ac6d92b24f0"

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - psycopg2
    - python
    - pytz

test:
  imports:
    - pgcopy

about:
  home: "https://pgcopy.readthedocs.io/en/latest/"
  license: "MIT"
  license_family: "MIT"
  license_file: "LICENSE.txt"
  summary: "Fast db insert with postgresql binary copy"
  dev_url: "https://github.com/altaurog/pgcopy"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - xhochy
